des:
Listen to 100.3 KROCK on your Amazon device(s)!

Once you've enabled the skill, saying "Alexa, OPEN one hundred point three k. rock" gets you right in.

100.3 KROCK, your go-to destination for all things classic rock. Dive into a sea of legendary guitar riffs, iconic vocals, and unforgettable melodies that have shaped generations.

Experience the power of classic rock like never before. Let the music take you on a journey through the greatest hits of all time. Stay connected, stay rockin', only on 100.3 KROCK - The Classic Rock Station.
